org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet

类 TelnetServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openintents.tools.simulator.model.telnet.TelnetServer

  • public class TelnetServer
extends java.lang.Object
    TelnetServer creates telnet connection with emulator's or Android's command port. Once we connect with command port we only need to send correct commands.
    作者:
    Josip Balic
